üí∞ 2. Tax and Financial Transparency

CivicVerse includes:
	‚Ä¢	A community wallet
	‚Ä¢	A built-in decentralized exchange (DEX)
	‚Ä¢	Monero mining integration (optional)

These tools exist for educational and simulation purposes. All real-world financial outcomes are the sole responsibility of the node runner or user.

We encourage all users to:
	‚Ä¢	Report taxable income in their jurisdiction
	‚Ä¢	Track wallet activity through auto-logging tools
	‚Ä¢	Use transparent wallets, CSV exports, and personal responsibility to stay compliant

We do not manage funds.
We do not take custody.
We do not offer financial advice.

This is a civic simulator, not a tax shelter.

